{"tid":652522,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國行程一問","createTime":"2018-05-04T01:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T09:36:16.000Z","uid":109650,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b71d1a05e9574d2b70c587c7d821ae023951fb6","tid":652522,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T01:48:37.000Z","msg":"同家人去 暫定去釜山<br />\n首爾就免啦 &nbsp;化妝品最撚憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鍾意食海鮮 唔會行山 家人行動不便 <br />\n行程想以食為主<br />\n所以巴絲有乜嘢意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n韓國嚟講 釜山啱唔啱玩？<br />\n定係濟洲好啲？<br />\n一定會去 應該係下個月尾去<br />\n/<br />\n聽人講鐵路唔會好複雜 想問係咪又係要買類似八達通嘅物體？<br />\n如果喺當地有冇得搭uber？ 因為之前喺馬來西亞搭uber平過的時候好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n/<br />\n兌錢係咪去到韓國先兌？<br />\n上網見人話轉咗美金再轉我覺得好煩<br />\n同埋喺轉兩次個差額我覺得會好唔抵<br />\n/<br />\n韓國消費係點？<br />\n釜山呢個係唔係同香港嘅旺角差唔多？<br />\n四日三夜夠唔夠玩？<br />\n預機票酒店連娛樂一人一萬夠唔夠？<br />\n/<br />\n有冇乜嘢景點係必去？ <br />\n我見到好多都話出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甚至如果想去埋濟州嘅話交通又應該點去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562342455df9c50412be9911ed5cba62cb217c2d","tid":652522,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d244640030fda4940c9d1a590f159a9c8b59ae49","tid":652522,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T03:23:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b1bc8f7e260e6ac233e3869c92022f03fd69491","tid":652522,"uid":11072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"濟州包車啱一家大細 釜山個人覺得麻麻地"},{"pid":"d2abf6ea43a0b79e7c4ddb94bac90ca3ca85ac9c",